768
01:14:50,111 --> 01:14:52,738
- Hurry and open up.
- What's the matter?

769
01:14:53,322 --> 01:14:54,740
My cousin fell and hurt himself.

770
01:15:00,079 --> 01:15:02,081
He's all right. Just let him rest.

771
01:15:09,630 --> 01:15:11,298
Where were you last night?

772
01:15:13,467 --> 01:15:14,885
I stayed with my cousin.

773
01:15:23,894 --> 01:15:25,688
Lock the door when you leave.

774
01:15:26,939 --> 01:15:28,858
Call me if anything happens.

775
01:16:31,879 --> 01:16:35,382
You don't get the death penalty
for shooting someone in a police station.

776
01:16:35,466 --> 01:16:38,844
A few years in the can
and you'll have earned your stripes.

777
01:16:38,928 --> 01:16:41,222
Today, people call you a boy,

778
01:16:41,305 --> 01:16:42,932
but tomorrow, they'll call you sir.

779
01:16:43,432 --> 01:16:46,685
It's your chance to make a name
for yourself, understand?

780
01:16:46,769 --> 01:16:48,437
Godfather, I'm afraid.

781
01:16:48,521 --> 01:16:52,525
Afraid? You drew lots
and now you say you're afraid?

782
01:16:52,608 --> 01:16:56,195
The other guys will kill you,
even if I let you off.

783
01:16:56,821 --> 01:16:59,698
Enough talk now!
Do it!

784
01:16:59,782 --> 01:17:02,034
Godfather, I'm really afraid.

785
01:17:02,118 --> 01:17:03,702
Chickenshit!

786
01:17:04,912 --> 01:17:06,372
Godfather.

787
01:17:07,873 --> 01:17:09,166
I gotta talk to you.

788
01:17:09,625 --> 01:17:12,586
- That's $23.50.
- Here's $30. Keep the change.

789
01:17:16,966 --> 01:17:18,092
Ah-Site.

790
01:17:19,009 --> 01:17:20,344
Brother!

791
01:17:23,013 --> 01:17:25,057
You're a different person
now that you're a father.

792
01:17:27,810 --> 01:17:30,938
I have no choice with a wife and baby.

793
01:17:31,021 --> 01:17:33,315
I'll do whatever it takes
to earn a living.

794
01:17:33,399 --> 01:17:34,859
Right.

795
01:17:35,359 --> 01:17:38,070
Take this money.
Go on.

796
01:17:38,154 --> 01:17:39,530
Why?

797
01:17:39,613 --> 01:17:41,073
I promised you.

798
01:17:42,700 --> 01:17:44,201
Sorry about last time.

799
01:17:45,077 --> 01:17:48,789
Find yourself
a fancy restaurant this time.

800
01:17:51,000 --> 01:17:53,544
And use the rest
to celebrate your son's birth.

801
01:17:55,087 --> 01:17:58,174
Remember: Don't let your wife's family
look down on you.

802
01:17:58,257 --> 01:18:00,217
Stick up for yourself. Understand?

803
01:18:00,301 --> 01:18:03,637
- Where'd you get it?
- That's not your concern!

804
01:18:13,856 --> 01:18:15,357
I'm not always gonna be around.

805
01:18:16,650 --> 01:18:18,277
Call Brother Wah, if you get in trouble.

806
01:18:20,321 --> 01:18:21,822
Brother?

807
01:18:21,906 --> 01:18:24,116
All these years
and we still never amounted to anything.

808
01:18:24,825 --> 01:18:26,619
I've been a pathetic big brother to you.

809
01:18:27,328 --> 01:18:29,163
- Don't say that--
- Let me finish!

810
01:18:37,004 --> 01:18:38,505
I know...

811
01:18:42,635 --> 01:18:46,805
you might have despised me
in the past.

812
01:18:51,185 --> 01:18:53,604
Fine!

813
01:18:54,647 --> 01:18:56,232
I deserved it.

814
01:18:57,650 --> 01:18:59,151
But in a couple days...

815
01:19:03,447 --> 01:19:06,992
when you read the papers and watch TV...

816
01:19:08,577 --> 01:19:12,456
you'll realize I'm not
a gutless coward after all.

817
01:19:16,418 --> 01:19:18,337
That I can be your big brother!

818
01:19:30,557 --> 01:19:33,018
Remember to tell everyone

819
01:19:33,894 --> 01:19:35,562
you've got a great big brother.

820
01:19:42,778 --> 01:19:44,280
Don't forget.

821
01:20:08,804 --> 01:20:10,306
Will these clothes do?

822
01:20:12,016 --> 01:20:14,059
You didn't sleep all night. Take a rest.

823
01:20:15,894 --> 01:20:17,313
I can't sleep.

824
01:20:27,489 --> 01:20:28,866
Don't worry.

825
01:20:29,700 --> 01:20:31,744
They're minor injuries. It's all right.

826
01:20:32,619 --> 01:20:35,372
You were lucky this time,
but what about next time?

827
01:20:36,999 --> 01:20:39,001
I've never thought about the next time.

828
01:20:40,377 --> 01:20:41,795
There's just one thing.

829
01:20:43,881 --> 01:20:45,591
When I go back to Hong Kong...

830
01:20:47,301 --> 01:20:49,219
I want you to go with me.

831
01:20:51,555 --> 01:20:56,185
Now that I've said it twice,
I can't take it back.

832
01:20:57,061 --> 01:20:58,854
What do you say?

833
01:21:07,946 --> 01:21:09,323
Come on.

834
01:21:12,743 --> 01:21:13,994
Come here.

835
01:21:17,122 --> 01:21:18,499
Stop it!

836
01:21:20,918 --> 01:21:22,503
I'll hit you!

837
01:22:06,588 --> 01:22:09,174
<i>Brother Wah, Fly gave me
a lot of money last night...</i>

838
01:22:10,509 --> 01:22:12,261
and told me to hold another banquet.

839
01:22:12,344 --> 01:22:15,556
He said I'd soon see
he wasn't a coward.

840
01:22:15,639 --> 01:22:17,141
Could you come right away?

841
01:22:18,767 --> 01:22:21,228
If you don't look out for him,
no one will.

842
01:22:31,989 --> 01:22:33,657
I'm on my way.

843
01:22:39,413 --> 01:22:40,539
Leaving again?

844
01:22:41,665 --> 01:22:44,460
It's nothing.
Just a friend who needs to talk.

845
01:22:45,210 --> 01:22:48,714
Oh, and I'll pick up
some medicine too.

846
01:23:09,985 --> 01:23:11,820
Anything you want me to get?

847
01:23:14,740 --> 01:23:16,158
I'll be back soon.

848
01:24:41,702 --> 01:24:42,744
Double eight.

849
01:24:42,828 --> 01:24:44,329
<i>Miss Cheung called.</i>

850
01:24:44,413 --> 01:24:45,998
<i>She said forget about the medicine.</i>

851
01:24:46,081 --> 01:24:49,585
<i>Just be careful
and come back as soon as you can.</i>

852
01:25:20,324 --> 01:25:22,034
I win again.

853
01:25:22,117 --> 01:25:23,785
Give me the money.

854
01:25:26,121 --> 01:25:27,539
Another game.

855
01:25:40,677 --> 01:25:43,597
Why didn't you tell me
you changed location, Tony?

856
01:25:45,140 --> 01:25:46,433
Get up.

857
01:25:46,516 --> 01:25:49,019
You sure you know the stakes here?

858
01:25:50,937 --> 01:25:52,689
Aren't I welcome here?

859
01:25:55,192 --> 01:25:58,111
Don't go losing
all your blood money to me.

860
01:25:58,987 --> 01:26:00,781
The guilt would drive me crazy.

861
01:26:03,075 --> 01:26:04,368
<i>You?</i>

862
01:26:05,077 --> 01:26:09,122
You're already crazy!
Why feel guilty now, you sorry bastard?

863
01:26:09,206 --> 01:26:10,415
- What are you saying?
- What?

864
01:26:10,499 --> 01:26:11,875
Huh?

865
01:26:11,958 --> 01:26:13,835
Let him be a big man for a few days.

866
01:26:13,919 --> 01:26:17,214
He's risking his life
for the chance.

867
01:26:17,297 --> 01:26:18,715
It's just a couple days.

868
01:26:18,799 --> 01:26:20,008
Right, Brother Fly?

869
01:26:24,513 --> 01:26:26,056
Come on.

870
01:26:26,515 --> 01:26:27,557
Mix up the tiles.

871
01:26:37,526 --> 01:26:38,777
Don't you know the rules?

872
01:26:38,860 --> 01:26:40,821
Do it again.

873
01:26:46,118 --> 01:26:47,077
Eight.

874
01:26:55,127 --> 01:26:56,586
Sorry about that.

875
01:26:57,170 --> 01:26:59,256
It just happened.

876
01:26:59,339 --> 01:27:00,966
Come on, let's play.

877
01:27:03,552 --> 01:27:05,345
- Stop messing around!
- Leave him alone!

878
01:27:06,680 --> 01:27:08,515
Let him be a two-day hero.

879
01:27:10,642 --> 01:27:12,894
A man of patience, eh?

880
01:27:12,978 --> 01:27:14,438
Well, fuck you!

881
01:27:23,822 --> 01:27:27,534
Think I won't dare
beat the crap out of you?

882
01:27:27,617 --> 01:27:29,077
Go ahead!

883
01:27:29,578 --> 01:27:30,996
Beat the crap out of me!

884
01:27:31,997 --> 01:27:35,333
Put me out of commission,

885
01:27:35,417 --> 01:27:37,544
and you'll have to take care of Big-Mouth Kay!

886
01:27:37,627 --> 01:27:39,379
Come on!

887
01:27:41,506 --> 01:27:42,883
Let me have it!

888
01:27:43,842 --> 01:27:45,093
Goddamn you!

889
01:27:45,635 --> 01:27:47,220
You little shit!

890
01:27:47,304 --> 01:27:49,097
Come on!

891
01:27:49,181 --> 01:27:51,099
One move and I'll blast him!

892
01:27:52,976 --> 01:27:55,187
Shoot me, if you dare!

893
01:27:55,270 --> 01:27:57,189
You daring me?

894
01:27:57,606 --> 01:27:59,608
Pull the trigger! Do it!

895
01:28:05,280 --> 01:28:06,740
No, don't shoot!

896
01:28:07,908 --> 01:28:10,076
No!

897
01:28:18,502 --> 01:28:20,128
Scared?

898
01:28:20,212 --> 01:28:21,713
Scared to death?

899
01:28:21,797 --> 01:28:23,381
Asshole!

900
01:28:23,465 --> 01:28:25,133
- I'll blow your head off!
- No!

901
01:28:26,468 --> 01:28:27,761
Don't shoot, Big Brother!

902
01:28:28,261 --> 01:28:32,557
I'd like to shoot you,
but you're not even worth the bullet.

903
01:28:35,602 --> 01:28:37,270
Here's the money I owe you.

904
01:28:38,313 --> 01:28:39,731
Pick it up.

905
01:28:41,191 --> 01:28:44,361
Pick it up.
This is your last chance.

906
01:28:44,444 --> 01:28:46,613
Pick it up or I'll shoot!

907
01:28:52,327 --> 01:28:53,703
"Thank you, Big Brother."

908
01:28:56,498 --> 01:28:58,917
Thank you, Big Brother.

909
01:29:03,505 --> 01:29:07,133
You've got your fancy suits and cell phones,
but so what?

910
01:29:08,426 --> 01:29:09,928
Look at your big brother now.

911
01:29:12,764 --> 01:29:13,974
You can go to hell!

912
01:29:26,111 --> 01:29:27,904
We're in this for the money, right?

913
01:29:27,988 --> 01:29:30,782
Why not take what he owes me?

914
01:29:30,866 --> 01:29:32,450
Take it and go dancing.

915
01:29:37,122 --> 01:29:40,375
Is this how you treat
your big brother?

916
01:29:53,597 --> 01:29:57,475
<i>Mom, I'm at the store.
Will you come meet me?</i>

917
01:29:58,018 --> 01:29:59,394
<i>What is it?</i>

918
01:29:59,477 --> 01:30:01,605
<i>Nothing. I know you don't like the heat,</i>

919
01:30:01,688 --> 01:30:03,356
<i>so I bought you an air conditioner.</i>

920
01:30:04,274 --> 01:30:07,569
<i>We've already got AC here.
You keep it.</i>

921
01:30:08,862 --> 01:30:11,406
<i>I can't come meet you. Your father's here.</i>

922
01:30:12,407 --> 01:30:14,743
He's your husband, not my father.

923
01:30:50,695 --> 01:30:52,697
When will you calm down and stop running?

924
01:30:53,198 --> 01:30:55,158
Why did you come out of hiding to see me?

925
01:30:55,909 --> 01:30:57,535
Why don't you leave me alone?

926
01:30:59,287 --> 01:31:02,415
Who's gonna look out for you
if I don't?

927
01:31:09,255 --> 01:31:11,549
Don't think this little stunt's
gonna make you a hotshot!

928
01:31:14,010 --> 01:31:15,178
Sure...

929
01:31:16,346 --> 01:31:19,265
everyone will say you've got guts
when you've done it.

930
01:31:21,184 --> 01:31:23,019
But no one will remember you next week!

931
01:31:24,688 --> 01:31:26,481
What'll become of you then?

932
01:31:26,564 --> 01:31:28,525
No one will even recognize you!

933
01:31:41,121 --> 01:31:43,081
I did a lot of things
for our godfather too.

934
01:31:46,167 --> 01:31:47,585
By the age of 14...

935
01:31:49,004 --> 01:31:50,797
I was already getting paid to kill.

936
01:31:54,342 --> 01:31:56,219
I've got more guts than most guys, right?

937
01:31:56,970 --> 01:31:59,514
But look at me now.
I'm just an ordinary guy!

938
01:32:00,098 --> 01:32:03,643
At least you were a hotshot
for a while!

939
01:32:04,894 --> 01:32:06,187
But what about me?

940
01:32:06,604 --> 01:32:08,106
What about me?

941
01:32:10,734 --> 01:32:13,695
Everyone looks down on me.
Does that make you happy?

942
01:32:14,446 --> 01:32:16,072
People think I'm nothing,

943
01:32:16,656 --> 01:32:19,617
like some stray dog
just following you around!

944
01:32:19,701 --> 01:32:21,077
Did you know that?

945
01:32:24,748 --> 01:32:27,709
I'd rather be a hero for one day,

946
01:32:27,792 --> 01:32:29,586
than go on being a fly all my life!

947
01:32:32,130 --> 01:32:34,549
Let me pull this off on my own, would you?

948
01:32:35,467 --> 01:32:36,885
Just this once!

949
01:32:51,524 --> 01:32:52,859
Okay.

950
01:32:55,528 --> 01:32:57,238
If you've already made up your mind...

951
01:32:58,573 --> 01:33:00,075
I'm going with you.

952
01:33:01,534 --> 01:33:03,179
If they shoot you down,
I'll finish the job.

953
01:33:03,203 --> 01:33:06,081
Stop being so good to me!

954
01:33:10,376 --> 01:33:12,128
I can't pay you back.

955
01:33:13,838 --> 01:33:15,799
Let's not talk about that now.

956
01:33:15,882 --> 01:33:17,967
If you're going, I'm going!

957
01:33:19,761 --> 01:33:23,306
But if you don't, I'll take you
back to Lantau Island with me.

958
01:33:26,935 --> 01:33:28,561
I'll take care of whatever comes up.

959
01:33:36,027 --> 01:33:38,655
Okay, okay.

960
01:33:40,031 --> 01:33:41,449
I'll go back with you.

961
01:33:57,715 --> 01:34:00,718
Hey, why you looking so ragged?

962
01:34:01,219 --> 01:34:03,304
Say hi to my big brother.

963
01:34:04,931 --> 01:34:08,393
Don't be so stingy.
Give the dog some.

